  Version bump for Gnome 3.16.

  07 Jun 2015; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org>
  adwaita-icon-theme-3.14.1.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #534012

  29 Mar 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org>
  adwaita-icon-theme-3.14.1.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #534012).

*adwaita-icon-theme-3.14.1-r1 (22 Mar 2015)

  22 Mar 2015; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  +adwaita-icon-theme-3.14.1-r1.ebuild:
  Stop installing the /usr/share/cursors/xorg-x11/default symlink, it messes up
  cursors in some non-GNOME desktop environments (bug #543488). Instead, rely
  on env variables set by the session; for GNOME, make sure you have
  >=gnome-session-3.14.0-r2

  15 Mar 2015; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> adwaita-icon-theme-3.14.1.ebuild:
  x86 stable, bug 534012

  15 Mar 2015; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> adwaita-icon-theme-3.14.1.ebuild:
  ppc64 stable, bug 534012

  15 Mar 2015; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> adwaita-icon-theme-3.14.1.ebuild:
  ppc stable, bug 534012

  14 Mar 2015; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> adwaita-icon-theme-3.14.1.ebuild:
  amd64 stable, bug 534012

  03 Mar 2015; Yixun Lan <dlan@gentoo.org> adwaita-icon-theme-3.14.1.ebuild:
  add arm64 support, tested on A53 board

  30 Dec 2014; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> adwaita-icon-theme-3.14.1.ebuild:
  gnome-base/librsvg is needed for this icon pack (#533978 by William Throwe)

  28 Dec 2014; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org>
  adwaita-icon-theme-3.14.1.ebuild:
  Add ~hppa keywords to allow adding to gtk+, see bug #533848.

*adwaita-icon-theme-3.14.1 (21 Dec 2014)

